content:
Here is a list of authors who have written about the Canary Islands:

* John Keats
* Robert Louis Stevenson
* Percy Bysshe Shelley
* Jorge Luis Borges
* Vicente Aleixandre
* Gustavo Adolfo Bécquer
* Fray Luis de León
* José Martínez Ruiz (Azorín)
* Blas de Otero
* José Agustín Goytisolo
* Francisco de Quevedo
* Francisco de Paula Santander
* Rosalía de Castro
* Luis Cernuda

This is not an exhaustive list and there are likely many more authors who have written about the Canary Islands. These authors may have written poetry, fiction, non-fiction, and other forms of writing that mention the Canary Islands.
